how to adjust a rca hdtv press menu arrow down to video arrow right for video choices arrow down to the video choice you want to choose arrow right to select it arrow left right to adjust it notice that each action switches you from arrow up down to arrow left right that's how most manufacturers design their menu systems sometimes they use the enter key to enter into a setting anything else requires an rca tv tech to access the service menu you can ruin an otherwise good tv getting into that part of the system Dance Dance Revolution EXTREME (North America) Dance Dance Revolution ULTRAMIX Mouse (computing) Television DVD Pump It Up DDRMAX2: Dance Dance Revolution Dance Dance Revolution ULTRAMIX 2 DDRMAX2: Dance Dance Revolution 7thMIX Dance Dance Revolution EXTREME DDRMAX: Dance Dance Revolution 6thMIX Dance Dance Revolution DDRMAX: Dance Dance Revolution High-definition television Windows XP PlayStation Portable Screenshot Greatest (Duran Duran) Windows 2000 Option key NTSC IPod SCART IBM PC keyboard Laserdisc Xbox Teletext Single Transferable Vote Digital television Computer keyboard Embedded system Avro Arrow Dance Dance Revolution 4thMIX Nintendo Entertainment System Windows Vista AS/400 Command Language Gradius S__CAM Danger Hiptop Tales of Destiny Vector (spatial) Keyboard layout TRS-80 NBC Common User Access Combo box Lunar: Dragon Song RCA Arrow's impossibility theorem System/36 Atari 8-bit family Videocassette recorder Super Nintendo Entertainment System ITunes System/34 Musical Instrument Digital Interface Elevator AmigaOS Hard disk BS Zelda: Kodai no Sekiban Context menu Federal Standard 1037C Floppy disk Verizon Wireless Microprocessor Traffic light Voting system AppleScript Dance Dance Revolution 2ndMIX Dance Dance Revolution KONAMIX Sonic the Hedgehog 2 Emacs Amstrad CPC Vim (text editor) Unicode Mac OS X v10.4 Federal Communications Commission Password Microeconomics Vertical service code Quicksort Nintendo DS TRS-80 Color Computer EXpanded MultiPlayer